  "detailed_description": "<h1>💟Add in WishList!!💟</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>💗Taiwan Love Story ⁵💗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/0cdd6ed7008b84b39ec47e78ee78bf13.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/0cdd6ed7008b84b39ec47e78ee78bf13.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/0cdd6ed7008b84b39ec47e78ee78bf13.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Story</h2>You're a college senior studying humanities at a university, and during a camping event held by your department, you meet five women from different parts of Taiwan. While you're hanging around the bonfire, a mysterious kiss leaves you lovestruck and yearning for more. Inspiration strikes, and you finally settle on a thesis topic: \"The Binary Equation of Love and Happiness.\"<br><br>In order to both finish your thesis and find true love, you set out on an adventure around the island. Along the way, you meet up with the women and experience a series of bittersweet romantic encounters bursting with youthful naivety. Your very own Taiwanese love story is about to begin...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/164d835046df99da0eb30814c3d34cc1.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/164d835046df99da0eb30814c3d34cc1.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/164d835046df99da0eb30814c3d34cc1.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/c41dc2bf74efeae08d36f6500153b7a1.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/c41dc2bf74efeae08d36f6500153b7a1.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/c41dc2bf74efeae08d36f6500153b7a1.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/bc782fe7bafd215ce053eeefea6fb9c2.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/bc782fe7bafd215ce053eeefea6fb9c2.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/bc782fe7bafd215ce053eeefea6fb9c2.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Light, fun simulation gameplay<br></li><li>Well-crafted, rich storylines for all 5 women<br></li><li>Exciting mini-games that match the game's theme<br></li><li>Full voice acting for the women!<br></li><li>Deep insights into local Taiwanese life and culture<br></li><li>Fully dynamic, immersive CGs<br></li><li>Download the free DLCs to unlock even more content!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/5351097092d1aa4bcf1bceabaad50c0d.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" 