n brought up in a strict household. She loves singing, but her father's plan has no room for art, so she has to give up on her dream...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/f6ed56e42ab056920e85b42a03bf03b1.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/f6ed56e42ab056920e85b42a03bf03b1.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/f6ed56e42ab056920e85b42a03bf03b1.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Zoe Hai<br>A lively, exuberant girl from Penghu. She loves diving and seems to have endless energy. Ain't nobody don't love Zoe!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/515548e4aee622a96d99c13f2bca64cf.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/515548e4aee622a96d99c13f2bca64cf.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/515548e4aee622a96d99c13f2bca64cf.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Lil' Blu<br>A hot betel nut babe from Taichung who acts like she won't let anyone get close. She's got a strong personality and is tough as shit, but deep down, she's just a girl who longs for affection.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/81d6b7c638c95e3265acf71ce754ccf9.poster.avif?t=1751546046\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/81d6b7c638c95e3265acf71ce754ccf9.webm?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976870/extras/81d6b7c638c95e3265acf71ce754ccf9.mp4?t=1751546046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sarah Wang<br>The co-owner of a small eel noodle shop in Tainan with her husband. Mrs. Wang is the essence of maternal warmth, and is a caring, captivating milf.",
